node.text:
Absolute Insanity! I can’t imagine how pumped @costadario was when he exited the second tunnel. 

#Repost @redbull
・・・
so @costadario just became the first person to fly a plane through a tunnel, wait! TWO tunnels and we are literally speechless 🤯

His unprecedented flight through Istanbul’s Çatalca Tunnels was seriously impressive with cross winds between the tunnels and air bumps inside them testing his skills - but ending the flight in the aviation history books was SO worth it 🙌

congrats on the @guinnessworldrecords Dario 👏

#redbull #givesyouwiiings #motorsports #stuntflying #flying #istanbul

node.text:
The first portion of the Loop Break 6 Plane Cross from the @usnavyblueangels. The pilots and the entire team are absolutely outstanding. They represent the @usnavy well, and I feel grateful that I got the opportunity to fly with them a couple weeks ago. 

#usnavyblueangels #viperdemoteam @viperdemoteam #justgonnasendit

node.text:
TLDR: I got in a mountain biking accident and I won’t be flying for 6-9 weeks. I’ll make a full recovery and finish the season with the @viperdemoteam #fullsendintoatree 

For those who haven’t heard, I got in a fairly serious accident last week while mountain biking. I had a front wheel catch while on a downhill trail, flipped over the front of my handle bars, and flew into a couple trees. 

The end results were about as good as I could hope for with an accident like that. Some minor fractures in my back, a few fractured ribs, and a bunch of scrapes and bruises. The back fractures won’t have any lasting affect other than being painful for the next few weeks. I’ve had plenty of fractured ribs, so I’m familiar with how bad those suck.

All in all I’m very grateful and fortunate to come out of such a bad accident with no permanent injuries. My doctors, nurses, techs, leadership, friends, family, and especially @drb_emergency have all been incredible. #stillgonnasendit

node.text: Gotta love 9G’s for 20+ seconds at a few hundred feet off the ground. This is one of the more challenging maneuvers physically. Gotta make sure your G-strain and breathing are on point or else you’ll put yourself in a bad spot real quick. This video was from Oshkosh last week. @viperdemoteam #viperdemoteam @eaa #eaa #eaaairventure

node.text:
Just finished up a long 2 week demo trip @fargoairsho and @eaa air venture in Oshkosh. It was our whole teams first trip to Osh, and to say it’s overwhelming is an understatement. An amazing lineup and the atmosphere was incredible. Looking forward to going next year in an RV-8 and experiencing the show from a tent! #viperdemoteam @viperdemoteam #eaa #eaaairventure #eaaoshkosh #fargoairsho 

📸: @ktmrider591
